-- Batista Plans to Sell 49% of AUX for Up to $2 Bln, Folha Says
-- B y   P e t e r   M i l l a r d
-- 2012-06-14T01:47:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-14/batista-plans-to-sell-49-of-aux-for-up-to-2-bln-folha-says.html
Brazilian billionaire  Eike Batista 
said Wednesday he plans to sell a 49 percent stake in his AUX
gold business for as much as $2 billion, Folha de S. Paulo
reported on its website.  Batista is negotiating with five separate buyers and
expects to conclude the sale in September, Folha said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Peter Millard in Rio de Janeiro at 
 pmillard1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
